The task is to create a converter of a file in csv format to html format. 
The converter is to meet the following assumptions: 
The first row of the csv file contains column headers. 
The number of columns and rows is not limited. The number of columns in each row is identical. 
The code of the table can be found at: 
https://www.w3schools.com/html/html_tables.asp 
Load all the lines from the csv file. 
Divide each line into columns 
Mark the first line with special formatting as a header 
Label the remaining lines with formatting alternating light dark
